## Code (in java )

class Solution {
    public int totalMoney(int n) {
        int weekStart=1;
        int day=0;
        int total=0;
       for(int i=1;i<=n;i++){
        total+=weekStart+day;
        day++;
        if(day==7){
            day=0;
            weekStart++;
        }
       }
       return total;
    }
}

## Code complexities :-

1. Time complexity :- O(n)
2. Space complexity :- O(1)
